('I11', 'iPhone 11 64GB', 1000, '0.00', 'Apple has officially launched a trio of iPhone 11 super products, in which the 64GB iPhone 11 version has the cheapest price but is still upgraded as strongly as the iPhone XR launched before.', '<div>\r\n	Powerful upgrade of the camera</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Talking about upgrades, the camera is the most improved point on the new iPhone generation.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Phone iPhone 11 64GB | Colorful design</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	If before the iPhone XR had only one camera, now with the iPhone 11 we will have up to two cameras on the back.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Phone iPhone 11 64GB | Rear camera</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	In addition to the main camera, which still has a resolution of 12 MP, we will have an extra wide-angle camera with the same resolution.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Phone iPhone 11 64GB | Portrait mode photo</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Portrait shot with iPhone 11</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	According to Apple, switching between the two lenses will not change the color of the image.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Phone iPhone 11 64GB | Portrait mode photo</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Portrait mode shot with iPhone 11</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	This is something that is considered a turning point because Android smartphones with many cameras today will often have color deviations when switching between lenses, which is quite uncomfortable for users.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Phone iPhone 11 64GB | Photos taken with Deep Fusion</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Photos taken with Deep Fusion</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Besides, with the iPhone 11, this will be the first time Apple has equipped its iPhone with night photography capabilities.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Phone iPhone 11 64GB | Photo taken with Night Mode Photo taken with Night Mode</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Photo taken with Night Mode</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	According to experience, this feature works very effectively, especially in extremely low-light environments.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Phone iPhone 11 64GB | Photo taken with the rear camera</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Activating the night mode will be decided by the iPhone itself, you just need to pick up the camera and shoot, very simple.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Phone iPhone 11 64GB | Super wide-angle mode shot</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Super wide-angle mode shot</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	This year Apple has also upgraded the front camera resolution to 12 MP instead of 7 MP like the previous generation.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	The front camera also has a smart feature, when you rotate the phone horizontally it will automatically activate the wide-angle selfie mode so you can take photos with more people.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Phone iPhone 11 64GB | Selfies with the front camera</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	In addition, Apple also introduced slow motion video recording for the front camera, something Apple has never equipped with previous iPhones.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	See also: Detailed evaluation of iPhone 11: Turning into a &#39;storm&#39; or a &#39;spray bomb&#39;?</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	World leading powerful performance</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Every time a new iPhone is released, Apple gives users an experience of &quot;unprecedented&quot; performance.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Phone iPhone 11 64GB | Experience gaming on iPhone 11</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	On the new iPhone 11, Apple upgraded its chip to the very powerful Apple A13 Bionic generation.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Phone iPhone 11 64GB | Antutu Benchmark Performance Score</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	This iPhone is also upgraded to 4 GB RAM instead of 3 GB like the previous generation.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Phone iPhone 11 64GB | Manipulation experience</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	At the above configuration level, the phone plays well with today&#39;s popular games in a smooth and stable way. Every operation on the new iPhone also gives a fast response speed that you will almost not feel the lag even after using it for a long time.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Phone iPhone 11 64GB | Gaming experience</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	See also: iPhone 11 durability test: Scratching, heating and bending</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	The iOS 15 version (December 2021) that comes with this iPhone is also equipped with more features to help you use your iPhone more efficiently.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Phone iPhone 11 64GB | Fashion Designer</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Face ID on iPhone 11 is also improved to be able to recognize at more angles and respond faster.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Design changes in a positive direction</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	We will have a finished glass back and Apple says that they have used the most durable glass ever for this iPhone.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Phone iPhone 11 64GB | Design dual camera cluster on the back</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	The dual camera on the new iPhone is also redesigned and the good news is that it will be less protruding than on the previous iPhone XR.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Phone iPhone 11 64GB | Fashion Designer</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	The highlight of the large camera cluster on the back will help others easily recognize that you are using an iPhone 11 in your hand.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Phone iPhone 11 64GB | SIM tray</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Apple&#39;s traditional apple logo has now been moved to the center of the large face instead of being skewed towards the top edge like previous iPhone models.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Phone iPhone 11 64GB | IP68 . water resistance</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Apple says it has perfected on the new iPhone so that it gives better water resistance and users can rest assured about that.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Best battery life ever</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	When it comes to iPhone 11 battery life, many people wish it had a battery as good as the iPhone XR (which has the best battery life of any modern iPhone).</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Phone iPhone 11 64GB | Battery life</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	However, you will have an even better machine.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Phone iPhone 11 64GB | Modern design</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	According to Apple, the new iPhone will have an hour longer battery life than the iPhone XR.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Phone iPhone 11 64GB | Dark Mode interface</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	So with the new iPhone, you can completely use the device for up to 2 days without worrying about the device running out of battery midway.</div>\r\n', '2023-06-03 07:56:43', 123, 'iphone-11-trang-200x200.jpg', 'C001'),
('I14', 'iPhone 14 128GB ', 1800, '0.00', 'iPhone 14 128GB is considered an explosive smartphone model of the apple house in 2022,', '<div>\r\n	Impressive with youthful appearance, quality screen accompanied by improvements in operating system and image processing algorithms, making the machine a name that attracts many users&#39; attention at the time of launch. .</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	iPhone 14 has a premium design</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	With the standard version, the Apple house retains the same design compared to its predecessor, still a flat back and a square frame to help the device become more modern.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Modern Design - iPhone 14 128GB</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	iPhone 14 has a horizontal size of 71.5 mm, so it can easily fit in the palm of your hand every time you use it, which makes the phone more suitable for a wider range of users, including friends. woman with small hands.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Camera - iPhone 14 128GB</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	The back of the phone is designed from tempered glass and finished in a smooth style, in my opinion, this approach makes the iPhone 14 look more attractive, besides it is also quite durable. Better scratch resistance.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Tempered glass back - iPhone 14 128GB</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	There is a small note in the design that the device is quite easy to stick to fingerprints, which is even more obvious in bold color versions such as black and red, and in light color versions such as blue, white and purple. pale, this is also improved.</div>\r\n', '2023-06-03 07:54:37', 123, 'iPhone-14-thumb-do-600x600.jpg', 'C001'),
('I14P', 'iPhone 14 Pro 128GB', 1900, '0.00', 'iPhone 14 Pro 128GB - The most anticipated smartphone from Apple in 2022,', '<div>\r\n	This time Apple brings us a version with a new notch design, powerful configuration thanks to Apple A16 Bionic chip and camera cluster with upgraded resolution up to 48 MP.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Elegant and distinctive design</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Coming to the design of this year&#39;s iPhone 14 Pro, the company retains the inherent features from previous generations, still carrying in itself a square appearance with flat beveled edges and back. Currently, the user&#39;s taste for this design is still very high, so in my opinion, this will still be a trending phone for many years to come.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Luxury Design - iPhone 14 Pro 128GB</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	The phone&#39;s frame is made of stainless steel and has a glossy finish, which makes the device durable as well as adds to the elegance. Every time I tilt the camera through many different angles, I find this frame more attractive thanks to its extremely interesting reflective ability.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Shiny frame - iPhone 14 Pro 128GB</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	After a while of use, I find this frame is quite easy to stick to fingerprints, using the phone with sweaty hands will also become a bit more difficult because the device is quite slippery at this time. To overcome the above two things, users can also use additional cases to ensure the most convenient use process.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Easy to stick to fingerprints - iPhone 14 Pro 128GB</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	As for the back, the main structural material will be tempered glass and finished with a rough finish to give it a more premium look, I feel that this roughening has also significantly overcome the problem of fingerprints compared to with glossy back on iPhone 14.</div>\r\n', '2023-06-03 07:52:41', 212, 'iphone-14-pro-vang-thumb-600x600.jpg', 'C001'),
('I14PM', 'iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB', 2000, '0.00', 'iPhone 14 Pro Max, a world-class smartphone product, was launched by Apple in September 2022.', '<div>\r\n	The device is equipped with an extremely powerful Apple A16 Bionic chip, accompanied by a new screen design, promising to bring new experiences to iPhone users.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Durable premium design</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	This year&#39;s iPhone will inherit the features from the brother iPhone 13 Pro Max, will still be a stainless steel frame and tempered glass back combined with a modern square shape through flat shaping at the edges and corners. back part.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Luxury Design - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	This year&#39;s Pro series was launched with many color options and the most prominent of which is probably the Deep Purple (purple) version, because this is a new color, it brings quite high recognition.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	New colors - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Featured with new screen design</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	The most impressive feature on this year&#39;s iPhone phones lies in the screen design, it is easy to see that the company has also removed the traditional rabbit ear cluster over many generations of iPhone with an extremely fancy new shape.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	New notch design - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Compared to this year&#39;s notch-shaped notch cluster, there is a relatively good area-saving part, but when compared to the &quot;mole&quot; screen models, this is still not really an optimal thing for the screen part. But Apple knows how to take advantage of disadvantages to turn them into advantages in a spectacular way by inventing many interesting effects.</div>\r\n', '2023-06-03 07:48:04', 123, 'iphone-14-pro-max-den-thumb-200x200.jpg', 'C001'),
('IP9', 'iPad 9 WiFi 64GB', 500, '0.00', 'After the success of iPad 8, Apple has released the iPad 9 WiFi 64GB tablet - the next version of the 10.2-inch iPad series,', '<div>\r\n	It basically inherits the strengths from previous versions and improves performance and user experience to help the needs of entertainment and work more convenient and flexible.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	The familiar design of the iPad series</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	iPad 9 owns a familiar rectangular shape with top and bottom edges, there are 2 main colors for you to choose from, elegant gray and trendy silver for you to choose according to your preferences.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Elegant, luxurious design - iPad 9 WiFi 64GB</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	The shiny aluminum outer shell, durable, good bearing and heat dissipation, comprehensively protects the internal components and increases the aesthetics of the product.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Durable Minimalist Case - iPad 9 WiFi 64GB</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Design the Home button in the middle of the bottom edge of the screen for quick action when needed. Touch ID fingerprint sensor is integrated in the Home key, allowing you to unlock quickly and securely.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Fingerprint Sensor - iPad 9 WiFi 64GB</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	The display is clear</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Featured with a screen size of up to 10.2 inches for a wider content display area, users can monitor entertainment programs, handle documents more conveniently.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Crisp 10.2-inch screen - iPad 9 WiFi 64GB</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Using a high-contrast Retina display, the 1620 x 2160 Pixels resolution reproduces images vividly. Moreover, the screen surface has an oleophobic coating to limit fingerprints, keeping the screen clean and clear.</div>\r\n', '2023-06-03 07:58:38', 123, 'iPad-9-wifi-trang-200x200.jpg', 'C002'),
('IPA5', ' iPad Air 5 M1', 900, '0.00', 'Compared to the iPad Air 5 M1 Wifi 64GB, the iPad Air 5 M1 Wifi Cellular 64GB has a significant difference', '<div>\n	a connection method when you can both use Wifi and use the mobile network normally but still give a very great experience.</div>\n<div>\n	Big screen, watch movies, work better</div>\n<div>\n	The tablet is equipped with a large screen up to 10.9 inches that is not too big but not too small for you to easily experience and use. Accompanying this Retina IPS LCD screen will bring you a better color experience.</div>\n<div>\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n	Super experience with big screen - iPad Air 5 M1 Wifi Cellular 64</div>\n<div>\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n	Trendy design</div>\n<div>\n	Compact design and squared Apple at the edges bring a sense of luxury and class, many users love this. The variety of colors will also help you have more suitable choices to use.</div>\n<div>\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n	Stylish Design - iPad Air 5 M1 Wifi Cellular 64GB</div>\n<div>\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n	Powerful performance</div>\n<div>\n	Powered by the Apple M1 chip and 8 GB of RAM, this iPad Air 5 M1 Wifi Cellular will have a tremendous power. It is up to 60% more powerful than its predecessor, promising to give you a super fast processing and working ability.</div>\n<div>\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n	Smart Features - iPad Air 5 M1 Wifi Cellular 64</div>\n<div>\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n	Thanks to running on the software version iPadOS 15 will have a lot of good features for you as well as optimize machine performance. There is also the ability to connect to Apple Pencil, Magic Keyboard, ... with extremely low latency.</div>\n<div>\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n	So much good stuff for an iPad Air 5 that will bring you the latest, most powerful and comfortable experiences whether for work or play.</div>\n', '2023-06-03 08:02:44', 212, 'ipad-air-5-wifi-cellular-pink-thumb-200x200.jpg', 'C002'),
('IPPM1', 'iPad Pro M1 11', 2000, '0.00', 'iPad Pro M1 11-inch WiFi 2TB tablet (2021) is introduced in 2 modern gray and silver colors, luxurious monolithic aluminum material and elegant and sophisticated design, suitable for any space.', '<div>\r\n	Possessing a Liquid Retina display with an 11-inch screen size, the tablet presents a frame of vibrant, vivid and true colors, sharp details on a resolution of 1668 x 2388 Pixels.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Quality display - iPad Pro M1 11 inch WiFi 2TB (2021)</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Thanks to a refresh rate of up to 120 Hz, touch and swipe the screen is extremely smooth, there is no delay in moving frames, so using the machine for online gaming needs, watching action movies will be great.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Work or play is perfect</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Powered by performance power thanks to Apple&#39;s 8-core Apple M1 chip, 8-core Apple GPU and 16GB of RAM, iPad easily conquers graphics tasks, or battles heavy games smoothly, multitasking with performance is really stable. It comes with 2 TB of internal memory creating a huge personal storage for all your favorite photos, videos and work documents.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	At the same time, to create convenience and entertainment performance, work better, you can combine your iPad with the 2nd generation Apple Pencil and Magic Keyboard on the desk.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Powerful, Versatile - iPad Pro M1 11-inch WiFi 2TB (2021)</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Combine with a good camera cluster</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Using the tablet to film, take photos, and take selfies is also impressive. The rear camera cluster focuses quickly, takes sharp pictures with a 12 MP main camera, a 10 MP super wide-angle camera and a TOF 3D LiDAR sensor.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Great camera - iPad Pro M1 11 inch WiFi 2TB (2021)</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	The 12-megapixel TrueDepth camera offers convenient FaceTime support and Center Stage, which automatically tracks motion to keep you in the center of the conversation. iPad Pro M1 also supports Apple face unlock, more security options and quick access on personal devices.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	In addition, using the device with high frequency will not be too concerned with the problem of rechargeable batteries, thanks to the equipped Li-Po battery with a large capacity of about 7538 mAh with a safe 20 W fast battery charging via the Type-C port, fast Quickly recharge the device when the power runs out.</div>\r\n', '2023-06-03 08:00:21', 123, 'ipad-pro-m1-11-inch-wifi-2tb-2021-bac-thumb-200x200.jpg', 'C002'),
('SSGS21', 'Samsung Galaxy S21 FE 5G', 1000, '0.00', 'Samsung Galaxy S21 FE 5G (6GB/128GB) được Samsung ra mắt với kiểu dáng vui thời thượng, cấu hình khỏe, chụp ảnh đẹp với bộ 3 camera', '<div>\r\n	Elegant appearance, fashion color</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Galaxy S21 FE 5G has a slim and light design with a thickness of 7.9 mm, a weight of only 177 grams, rounded edges for a harmonious and soft feel, combining trendy colors including purple, green, gray and white makes it easy for you to create your own personal style.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Samsung Galaxy S21 FE 5G (6GB/128GB) - Luxurious appearance, stylish color</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	The details are delicately finished, the aluminum chassis is quite light and durable, the back is made of plastic, the processing is light rough, the hand grip, when used a bit sticky with sweat but very easy to clean.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	The smartphone screen is covered with shiny Corning Gorilla Glass Victus, which is almost safe when dropped from a height of 2m (information from the manufacturer announced), effectively limiting scratches.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	On the side of the device, there are power buttons, smooth volume, sim slot on the bottom edge, located near the microphone, so when inserting the sim you need to pay attention to avoid confusing manipulation.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Switching to the back of the device, the rear camera arrangement in a vertical row is similar to the S21 version, the camera cluster is raised, can be scratched if placed on the table many times, so to better protect the lens, you Can use more cases, stickers.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Samsung Galaxy S21 FE 5G (6GB/128GB) - On the back of the device, how to arrange the rear camera in a vertical row</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	The product is designed to be waterproof and dustproof to IP68 standards, reducing the possibility of water and dirt ingress affecting the life and operation of the device, giving you confidence to carry your phone on daily journeys. as well as when traveling, working away from home.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	True viewing experience</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	With a size of 6.4 inches, quite thin borders, punch-hole front camera for spacious display space, you can see more details on the screen.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Support for modern screen technology Dynamic AMOLED 2X, Full HD + resolution, 120 Hz refresh rate, for detailed, smooth images, fresh colors, high contrast.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Samsung Galaxy S21 FE 5G (6GB/128GB) - Immersive viewing experience</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	With a maximum brightness of 1200 nits, both indoor and outdoor viewing provide good image quality. The phone integrates clear dual stereo speakers for a decent volume.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	In addition, below the screen there is an optical fingerprint sensor that allows quick fingerprint unlock, you can also choose to unlock with the front camera depending on the use situation.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Stable performance, smooth game play</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Powering the S21 FE is an Exynos 2100 CPU with a power that is considered equivalent to Snapdragon 888, so it will certainly not disappoint you when it meets from everyday tasks such as reading newspapers, watching movies to typing. Words in Word, Excel are smooth. Performance test with PCMark software (left) for 14,234 points, GeekBench 5 (right) for 745 single-core points and 2,183 multi-core points.</div>\r\n', '2023-06-03 08:10:40', 312, 'Samsung-Galaxy-S21-FE-vang-1-2-200x200.jpg', 'C003'),
('SSGZF4', 'Samsung Galaxy Z Fold4 5G 256G', 2000, '0.00', 'At the annual Samsung Unpacked event, the Samsung Galaxy Z Fold4 256GB was officially launched to the technology market,', '<div>\r\n	carrying many valuable improvements to help the Galaxy Z Fold become a better and better folding phone.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Exquisite folding design makes a difference</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Galaxy Z Fold4 (2022) launched with an almost unchanged appearance when compared to the Galaxy Z Fold3, if you just look at it, it will be difficult for you to distinguish these two products. The device still uses a durable Armor Aluminum frame, the secondary screen glass is Corning Gorilla Glass Victus +, the main screen glass is Ultra Thin Glass.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Make a difference with the folding and unfolding screen - Samsung Galaxy Z Fold4 256GB</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	And this is also the most durable folding phone in the smartphone world when combined with IPX8 water resistance, capable of being immersed in fresh water at a depth of up to 1.5 meters for up to 30 minutes* (the device is not capable of being submerged in water). dust resistance).</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	*Information provided by Samsung</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Waterproof phone - Samsung Galaxy Z Fold4</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	This year Z Fold4 has a more balanced design, the hinge and screen border are designed to be thinner, making the overall screen of the device 2.7 mm wider and the main screen 3 mm wider than its predecessor. . Although the number is not too large, with practical experience, this is an extremely valuable change and brings high efficiency.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	With the increased screen size, Fold4&#39;s secondary screen has made it easier to manipulate and type text, no longer experiencing sticky text like on the previous generation. With this screen ratio, it is still slightly higher than the average smartphone in the market.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Bigger Secondary Screen - Samsung Galaxy Z Fold4 256GB</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Samsung has changed the hinge structure on the Fold4, which gives a stronger opening and closing feeling. The device can be flexibly folded - opened at angles from 75 degrees to 115 degrees, giving you more angles to use the phone.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Change the hinge structure - Samsung Galaxy Z Fold4</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	With this flexible folding ability, you can place the device on a flat surface to take photos with creative angles to shoot TikTok or work as a &quot;mini laptop&quot;.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	See also: Flex Mode on Galaxy Z Fold4 and Z Flip4: A new trend and flexible lifestyle!</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Flex Mode on Samsung Galaxy Z Fold4</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Great screen, great experience</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Samsung Galaxy Z Fold4 has a 6.2-inch external secondary screen with HD + resolution. The 7.6-inch main screen supports a folding mechanism, using the brilliant Dynamic AMOLED 2X screen technology and a number of technologies such as support for a maximum brightness of 1200 nits, a 120 Hz refresh rate that can adapt depending on applications and settings.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Leading screen technology in the smartphone world - Samsung Galaxy Z Fold4</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	All of the above parameters make Fold4 a device with the best display capabilities on the market, with vibrant colors, flattering eyes, deep blacks and a screen that is also certified for eye protection to give you more peace of mind. when using the product for a long time.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	The Fold4&#39;s main screen size is almost the same as that of a tablet, giving you a larger display space, combined with exclusive optimized software, making the Galaxy Z Fold4 a 2-in-1 device. convenience period.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	This year Galaxy Z Fold4 focuses on software upgrades and user experience, with this new Fold version when you enter any application, the bottom of the screen will appear a similar Taskbar on the computer.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	The taskbar on the new generation Galaxy Z Fold - Samsung Galaxy Z Fold4</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	You can customize such as adding and removing applications on this toolbar, newly opened applications will also appear here. It will help you multitask faster, switch between applications more intuitive. You can drag and drop applications from the taskbar onto the screen to multi-window multitasking, split screen.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	This taskbar only appears on the main screen, the taskbar secondary screen will not appear, you will still use it as a regular smartphone.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	On the main screen, Galaxy Z Fold4 supports multitasking with up to 3 apps split screen (the secondary screen supports up to 2 apps), if you use a floating window, the number of windows will be increased. .</div>\r\n', '2023-06-03 08:12:31', 213, 'samsung-galaxy-z-fold4-kem-256gb-200x200.jpg', 'C003'),
('SSS23', 'Samsung Galaxy S23 5G Ultra 1T', 2000, '0.00', 'After nearly a year of waiting, the super product Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 1TB has finally been officially revealed', '<div>\r\n	With a range of industry-leading technologies, the highlight of which is the Snapdragon 8 Gen 2 chip, a 200 MP camera and comes with an integrated S Pen so you can freely draw or take notes. fast.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Shine with a luxurious eye-catching look</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	The front of Galaxy S23 Ultra has the characteristic Infinity-O design of the Galaxy S series phones so far, the screen is also curved to the sides to give users a better experience with wide screen space. in handle.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Luxury Design - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	The back is roughened from tempered glass material, so the Galaxy S23 Ultra looks more personal and offers better scratch resistance, fingerprint resistance, and dust resistance.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	The highlight is that the new generation S Pen on the Galaxy S23 Ultra is significantly improved to help users operate faster and more sensitive than previous generations in everyday tasks such as: Quick notes, support buttons. Photography support, presentation support, drawing,...</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Excellent display quality screen with high resolution</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	The Galaxy S23 Ultra screen has a size of 6.8 inches with a Dynamic AMOLED 2X panel capable of displaying images in a true and brilliant way, along with the display space that the device brings is extremely spacious. so you can fully enjoy all movies or manipulate games and draw comfortably.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Premium screen - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	The screen on this Samsung phone is considered excellent with 2K + resolution, 120 Hz refresh rate support for users to experience watching movies, playing games and surfing the web, ... extremely smooth.</div>\r\n', '2023-06-03 08:07:41', 212, 'samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-thumb-trang-200x200.jpg', 'C003');

